ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS (IRPR) in order to specify that “Employment and Social Development” has authority under the IRPR to fulfill certain responsibilities in administering the Temporary Foreign Worker Program by amending certain provisions of Division 3 of Part 11 of the IRPR to reflect the new department name and the new title of the Minister.
